title: Preseason Winners and Losers with Arif Hasan
itunes:title: Preseason Winners and Losers with Arif Hasan
description:
A room filled with only two heroes - Dan Hanzus and Gregg Rosenthal shuffle through the NFL news including Carson Wentz returning to practice and Cam Newton in COVID protocols. Arif Hasan joins the show to go over preseason winners and losers.
